# [PROGRAM_NAME] Decisions Log
# Slug: [program-slug]
# Created: [YYYY-MM-DD]
# Format: YYYY-MM-DD | TYPE | DESCRIPTION | CONTEXT
# Types: DECISION | RISK_ACCEPTED | ONE_WAY_DOOR | ESCALATED
#
# RULES:
# - Append only. Never modify or delete existing entries.
# - One event per line. No line wrapping — keep descriptions concise.
# - This file is queried, not fully loaded. grep-friendly by design.
# - DECISION: any direction set by the principal that governs future action
# - RISK_ACCEPTED: explicit acceptance of a named risk — requires principal sign-off
# - ONE_WAY_DOOR: any irreversible action taken — external comms, contractual, reputational
# - ESCALATED: items escalated and how they were resolved
#
# QUERY EXAMPLES:
#   All decisions:              grep "^[0-9].*DECISION" [program]-decisions.log
#   All accepted risks:         grep "RISK_ACCEPTED" [program]-decisions.log
#   One-way doors this year:    grep "^2026.*ONE_WAY_DOOR" [program]-decisions.log
#   Unresolved escalations:     grep "ESCALATED|UNRESOLVED" [program]-decisions.log
#
